Sentence: Phylogenetic analyses All concatenated ribosomal trees ( Fig. 1) used finished and permanent draft genomes downloaded ( September 2016) from IMG [ 41] to create reference datasets for 16 ribosomal proteins chosen as single - copy phylogenetic marker genes ( rpL2, rpL3, rpL4, rpL5, rpL6, rpL14, rpL15, rpL16, rpL18, rpL22, rpL24, rpS3, rpS8, rpS10, rpS17, rpS19).
